		    <td colspan=1 rowspan=1 bgcolor="white">
		      <center><h2><FONT color="#8B4513"><a name="DOWNLOAD">DOWNLOAD</a></font></h2></center>
		      <table bgcolor="white">
			  <tr><td>
			      <UL>
				<LI>Robusta is a seperate program for the Linux operating system and needs several programs to be installed: T-Coffee to combine the libraries and one or serveral genome alignment programs.</LI>
			      <li><a href="robusta" >Click here to download Robusta binary</a></li>
			      </UL>
			      
			    </td></tr>
		      </table>
		    </td>
		  </tr>

