		    <td colspan=3 bgcolor="white" valign="top">
		      <center><h2><FONT color="#8B4513"><a name="INSTALLATION">INSTALLATION</a></font></h2></center>
		      <table bgcolor="white">
			  <tr>
			    <td>
			      <P align="justify"><b>1-</b>Download the executable or use Git to get the source code of the current version: "git clone https://github.com/cbcrg/robusta.git"</P>
			    </td>
			  </tr>
			  <tr>
			    <td>
			      <P align="justify"><b>2-</b> If you downloaded the source code change into the g_coffee directory and type "make mode=release". </P>
			    </td>
			  </tr>
			  <tr>

			  </tr>
		      </table>
		    </td>
		    <td bgcolor="#FFEBCD"><br></td>
		  </tr>

